            <title>[CASSANDRA-6114] Pig with widerows=true and batch size = 1 works incorrectly</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-6114</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
